            "creation_date": 1434851905,
            "body": "<p>Use <code>Runtime.getRuntime().exec(\"javac SomeFile.java\")<\/code> to compile the Java files via the command line.<\/p>\n\n<p>If you're not sure if <code>javac<\/code> or <code>java<\/code> is in the PATH, try specifying the fully path directly (i.e. <code>C:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk1.8.0_xx\\bin\\javac<\/code>) or just ask the user where it is.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 30960574,
            "question_id": 30960204
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/147c5a9cc1feec049c50da791ac7d144?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 47283,
                "user_type": "registered",
